          </a>

          <a href="https://ilgiardinodelcorpo.it/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
